\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
Paper showing reallocation from enforcing to non-enforcing in second period,
 consistent with SV vs.
 Rt 128 story (citation)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Some theory showing potential advantages of not having non-competes
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
Allows for reallocation of skilled labor when uncertainty about firm 
